text: Jarosław Nowicki (born 2 May 1970) is a Polish rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bydgoszcz
